Project name		Predicting Customer Spending with Linear Regression
Duration		Aug 2025 ‚Äì Sep 2025
Description		This project involved analysing customer behaviour data to predict yearly spending based on features such as average session length, time on app, time on website, and length of membership. The project applied Simple and Multiple Linear Regression to understand which factors most influence customer spending and to provide actionable insights for improving mobile app or website engagement. Key focus was on data exploration, model training, evaluation, and interpretation of coefficients to support business decisions.
Technology Stack		Python, Pandas, NumPy
Responsibilities		‚Ä¢	Performed data analysis, visualization, and trained linear regression models to predict customer yearly spending. Evaluated model performance, interpreted coefficients for business insights, and documented results for clarity and reproducibility.



Use multi-linear regression to analyze the relationship of a product's price, advertisement cost, and the product sales number.
